text: Ðis sint þa landgemaro to cenigtune of temese stæðe on wulfrices broc uppan rige weorðe on þa ealdan dic of þære dic ut on Rige wurðe heal.
Þanne on þone rahhege andlang þæs hege on Bagganwurðe æfre Be efic<../images/tbar.gif>hit cymþ on sceaceling æcere.
Þonne ut on stanford þanne ut on temese on þone igoð ðwyres ofer berege on ceane wyllan and stremes ut temese andlang temese<../images/tbar.gif>hit cymð on hyrd ige þonne ut eft on wulfrices broc.
